  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the effect of intravenous human recombinant
      erythropoietin on the reperfusion injury at primary percutaneous coronary intervention in
      patients with acute myocardial infarction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
